@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_satifd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.15) + (v2 + 0.84 / v2 + 0.70)) - ((v0 + 0.52 / v0 + 0.49) + v1))
    v0 = wp.cos(v2)
    v0 = (v2 - ((v2 + 0.73 - v0 + 0.60) * 0.06))
    data[tid] = v0
